function
   highlights subsections of text

requires
   none
   
usage
   orange.print('<span class="xc-red">Pay attention</span>', vpos, hpos)
   
   VPOS
       -2 : top of the block
       -1 : last displayed line
        0 : current line
        1 : next displayed line
        2 : prompt
        
   HPOS
       -2 : prefix & newline
       -1 : prefix
        0 : newline
        1 : suffix
        2 : suffix & newline
